sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant FE as browser
    participant GW as api-gateway
    participant AUTH as auth-orchestrator
    participant SVC as user-service
    participant DB as user-db
    participant R as Redis
    participant NOTIF as notification-service
    participant SES as amazon-ses

    rect rgb(240,248,255)
    Note over FE,SES: 1. Login & Pre-checks

    FE->>GW: POST /auth/login { email, password }
    GW->>AUTH: login({ email, password })
    AUTH->>SVC: find_user_by_email(email)

    SVC->>DB: SELECT user WHERE email = ?<br/>AND deleted_at IS NULL AND password_voided_at IS NULL
    Note over DB: New columns: password_voided_at, password_changed_at<br/>password_voided_at IS NULL in query → voided users auto-rejected<br/>⚠ migration required
    DB-->>SVC: user row | null
    SVC-->>AUTH: user | RpcException(404)

    alt user not found | unverified | wrong password
        AUTH-->>GW: 401 Unauthorized
        GW-->>FE: 401 Unauthorized
    end

    Note over AUTH: bcrypt.compare OK ✓<br/>password age > 90 days → EXPIRED — proceed to token issuance
    end

    rect rgb(255,248,235)
    Note over FE,SES: 2. Token Generation

    AUTH->>AUTH: raw_token = randomBytes(32).hex()<br/>token_hash = SHA-256(raw_token)

    AUTH->>R: SET expired_reset:{token_hash} → user_id  EX 900
    Note over R: key   → expired_reset:{token_hash}<br/>value → user_id<br/>TTL   → 900s (15 min)
    R-->>AUTH: OK

    AUTH->>SVC: void password + record reset issuance
    Note over SVC: SET password_voided_at = NOW()<br/>SET password_reset_issued_at = NOW()
    SVC-->>AUTH: updated
    end

    rect rgb(240,255,245)
    Note over FE,SES: 3. Notify User

    AUTH-)NOTIF: emit('send_password_expiry_email') { to, reset_url }
    Note over NOTIF: Fire-and-forget ⚡ — reset_url carries raw_token (never in logs)<br/>⚠ Not yet implemented — needs new handler + template

    NOTIF->>NOTIF: render password-expiry email
    NOTIF->>SES: sendMail() via SMTP
    SES-->>NOTIF: 250 OK

    AUTH-->>GW: 200 Password expired — reset link sent to your email
    GW-->>FE: 200 Password expired — reset link sent to your email
    end
